 It\u2019s been a year of big changes for Micepad, with a new website, new features, and plenty of updates! Although December brings to mind holidays and merrymaking, our tech team has by no means slacked off!\u00a0<\/p><p class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">Following up on our newly implemented interactive module, we\u2019ve taken the time to tweak and further improve upon our current design.\u00a0<\/p><h2 class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\" data-css=\"tve-u-16ed95c31b3\">Small (but mighty!) new features for Q&amp;A<\/h2><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7db702 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a7db702\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"524\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/12\/QA-Update-1024x537.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2167\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/12\/QA-Update-1024x537.png 1024w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/12\/QA-Update-300x157.png 300w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/12\/QA-Update-768x402.png 768w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/12\/QA-Update-1536x805.png 1536w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2019\/12\/QA-Update.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-891bc1e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"891bc1e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><div class=\"thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element\"><h3 class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">New Stat Counter<\/h3><p class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">We\u2019ve added the count number for pending, approved and archived responses! The change may look small, but we\u2019ve found that it has a great impact on our users\u2019 capability to assess the popularity of topics. With this update, we\u2019ve taken more steps towards improving the measurability of our engagement metrics.<\/p><h3 class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">Moderation Toggle<\/h3><p class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">During many events, we\u2019ve noticed that the moderation setting was especially popular with users. Indeed, this extremely useful setting has been one of the most used since the start of Micepad. However, we also realised that plenty of users would double and even triple check to make sure that it was on, which was why we decided to ease their concerns by moving the button securely to the front!<\/p><h3 class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">New icon buttons<\/h3><p class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">Micepad has always aimed for a sleek and clean panel design that maximises utility and user-friendliness. In keeping with this goal, we\u2019ve switched the text buttons beside the messages to icons for not just a fresher look, but a more intuitive approach.\u00a0<\/p><p class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">Additionally, besides the append icon [+], we\u2019ve also included the \u2018screen\u2019 icon to push individual messages to the projector screen.<\/p><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba3f5f4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ba3f5f4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">New Profile Photo\/Initial Setting<\/h2><p class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\">Finally, we added a new setting that shows the poster\u2019s profile photo or initial on-screen.<\/p><p class=\"tve-droppable\" dir=\"ltr\"><em>Stay tuned for more Micepad updates!<\/em><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In the blink of an eye, 2019 is nearly over. It\u2019s been a year of big changes for Micepad, with a new [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2333,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[134],"tags":[139],"class_list":["post-2158","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-product-updates","tag-product-updates"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2158","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2158"}],"version-history":[{"count":8,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2158\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3458,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2158\/revisions\/3458"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2333"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2158"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2158"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad